Manx: Slattys son coyrt pooar dy vooadaghey yn thie dy Hauchys son mee-cheeayllee cour-y-traa, 1866, as son ymmydyn elley;
English: The Temporary Lunatic Asylum Act, 1866. (An act for giving power to enlarge the temporary asylum for lunatics for other uses.

Manx: Slattys son coyrt pooaraghyn dy Chaghlaa Thallooyn Chillagh as Thallooyn elley.
English: The exchange of Glebe and other Lands Act 1866. (An act to give powers to exchange Glebe Lands and other Lands.
